<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1909-09-14T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1909-09-14T00:00:00-05:00" n="14" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d14">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 534/102.</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Stutesman</persName>
                                to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Pharaphrase.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">La
                                    Paz</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1909-09-14"><hi rend="italic">September 14,
                                    1909</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>Reports that Bolivia will accept award and thereby satisfy Government of
                            Argentina; that Bolivia is treating with Peru for modification of
                            boundary line, and that they are not far apart in their respective
                            contentions.</p>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>